WF-003 | Open Create Closure form | actor: Accounting user | branch: none | terminal: + Create Closure | on_success: opens Create_Closure_Form
WF-004 | Create Closure | actor: Accounting user | branch: none | terminal: Create Closure | on_success: prevents journal entries from being posted for dates on or before the closing date (locks completed accounting periods)
